attributes.title: ✨Simpsons ✨
attributes.review: So I downloaded this app because someone told me that the Simpsons ending was gonna happen in real life in 2020 or 2021 and they said that if I downloaded this app it’ll let me know what’s going to happen at the end of 2020. So I put my phone down and rode my skateboard fifty miles per hour to feed my pet dinosaur her name is Roxy and I looked at her beautiful china plate and it was dirty so I cleaned it then I found out that she has no more food left so now I have to go to Jurassic park and buy her some camel toes then I saw this rabbit talking to me and I followed it down a rabbit hole and we had a tea party with the mad hatter and I realized that it was midnight and I haven’t fed my pet dinosaur yet so I rode my skateboard home with the speed of light per second. I was just in time to feed Roxy and I looked at the calendar and tomorrow was the day I meet her family for the first time and I completely forgot to memorize my dinosaurs and I didn’t want to disappoint Roxy so I took my scooter and my laptop and I went in the woods next to the swimming pool at the school and i began memorizing the dinosaurs until I saw a dog and a unicorn and I touched the unicorn and I couldn’t take my hands off it and it took me to the underworld I saw Hades and Persephone and it was an awesome experience better than Hawaii and the Turks I saw Michael Jackson there he was performing a live concert. After the concert I went back to the woods next to the pool at the school to memorize my dinosaurs and then I went on Quizlet and it started to freeze and glitch and this app was the reason why MY COMPUTER FROZE AND I NEVER FOUND OUT WHAT HAPPENED TO THE SIMPSONS AND IT MADE ME LATE TO MY BAPTISM .✨🤡👄😊🏖🥰🥰🙃😔🤮🏖😍🤣💀😭🥺💞👅☺️🌅⛰🤢👀🥳🦋👁💖🤸🏾‍♀️🛹💃🏻🥩🌈.
